      "span_text": "PCR primers were: for nucA (5′-CCATCAATCAGCGTG-CATTTAC-3′ and 5′-TGTTGTTGTAGGAGAGTGCATATT-3′); for nuiA (5′-GAGTGAGTCTGAATACCCATTTGA-3′ and 5′-TCTTGTCCGTGA-CCTGTTTG-3′); for slr0664 toxin (5′-GCAAAAAGGCGTCATTAGT-3′ and 5′-AATCGGTAGCCAGAACTTT-3′); for control housekeeping gene rnpB  ) (5′-CGTTAGGATAGTGCCACAG-3′ and 5′-CGCTCTTACCGCACCTTTG-3′)."
